= Locations =

'''Dragon Warrior II''' features an expanded world compared to the original, with multiple continents and islands to explore.

__TOC__

== World Overview ==

The game spans two major regions:
* '''Midenhall Region''' - Main continent with Midenhall, Cannock, and Moonbrooke
* '''Greater World''' - Expanded area with Alefgard and new lands

